%package podbc
Summary: PostGres ODBC based connectivity module for Meta-HTML.
Group: Applications/WWW
Requires: metahtml

%description podbc
Using modpodbc.so, you can enable the connection of Meta-HTML to PostGres
databases, by simply saying <sql::set-datbase-type podbc>.

%files podbc
